---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import SectionHead from "@components/sectionhead.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Service Level Agreement - DevArmor"
  description="DevArmor's Service Level Agreement outlining uptime commitments, support response times, and service credits."
  canonicalURL={new URL("/terms/sla", Astro.site).toString()}>
  <Container>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <SectionHead
        title="Service Level Agreement"
        description="What you can expect from our platform and what happens if things go wrong"
      />

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mt-8">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Welcome to DevArmor! We're committed to providing a secure, fast, and
          reliable experience. This SLA outlines what you can expect from our
          platform, and what happens if things go wrong.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6">
          1. Uptime Commitment
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          We aim to maintain <strong>99.9% uptime</strong> for our core platform
          services each month (excluding scheduled maintenance or force majeure events).
          That's less than ~43 minutes of unplanned downtime per month.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6">
          2. Support Response Times
        </h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
          <table
            class="min-w-full border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
              <tr>
                <th
                  class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">
                  Severity Level
                </th>
                <th
                  class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">
                  What It Means
                </th>
                <th
                  class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">
                  Initial Response Time
                </th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody
              class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 divide-y divide-gray-300 dark:divide-gray-600">
              <tr>
                <td
                  class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">
                  Critical (System Down)
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Platform is unavailable or severely impacted
                </td>
                <td
                  class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  &lt; 2 business hours
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td
                  class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">
                  Major (Partial Disruption)
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Key features not working as expected
                </td>
                <td
                  class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  &lt; 4 business hours
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td
                  class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">
                  Minor (General Issues)
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Bugs, usability, or informational questions
                </td>
                <td
                  class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  &lt; 1 business day
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Support is provided during business hours (9am–6pm PT, Monday–Friday).
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6">
          3. Maintenance Windows
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          We perform routine maintenance during off-peak hours (usually weekends
          or late evenings PT). We'll do our best to notify you at least 24
          hours in advance if there's potential impact.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6">
          4. Service Credits
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          If we fall below 99.9% uptime in a given month, you may be eligible
          for a pro-rated service credit on your next invoice. Just email us at <a
            href="mailto:support@devarmor.com"
            class="text-[#f44b88] hover:underline">support@devarmor.com</a
          > within 30 days of the incident.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6">
          5. Limitations
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
          This SLA does not apply to:
        </p>
        <ul
          class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Issues caused by your own network or internet provider.</li>
          <li>Third-party integrations outside our control.</li>
          <li>Beta features or sandbox environments.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6">
          6. Need Help?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          We're always here to help. Contact our team at <a
            href="mailto:support@devarmor.com"
            class="text-[#f44b88] hover:underline">support@devarmor.com</a
          > and we'll get you sorted.
        </p>

        <div
          class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border-l-4 border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 p-6 mt-8 rounded-r-lg">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 italic">
            This SLA is informational only and doesn't create a legal warranty
            or guarantee. We may update it from time to time, and we'll post any
            changes here.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>

